{"tid":1461091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再屌機場，放工自然多人","createTime":"2019-08-13T06:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:26.000Z","uid":193565,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61f6be0a8f2f4ba9e5a8a1102d0875173ed7912a","tid":1461091,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:11:58.000Z","msg":"番緊工呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be5f3598f237779a6a68d8fb36c7fda2988dfe6","tid":1461091,"uid":248404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"尋日唔洗番？"},{"pid":"16b9626b79579b42560de279596f16c28cb7176e","tid":1461091,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6be5f3598f237779a6a68d8fb36c7fda2988dfe6","tid":1461091,"uid":248404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"尋日唔洗番？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"尋日真係好多人特登拎SL AL"},{"pid":"222c1c5b2e0d3f6a2c6ab85d79ab82512b9ca3fd","tid":1461091,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係地鐵放tear gas 係好大張牌<br />\n文宣 貼多啲post係連儂牆 </span></span>"},{"pid":"edc43d7a1cb6a7d61d48f6383a7146385efd9af1","tid":1461091,"uid":254361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n行動前，用腦諗下，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n同埋連登被滲透之下<br />\n各種謠言滿天飛，更加要冷靜思考<br />\n要多方面去驗證嗰篇文是否真實<br />\n再去諗下佢發呢個信息個目的係乜嘢<br />\n諗下佢背後有沒隱藏的意思（例如恐慌、煽動、造謠）<br />\n<br />\n和理非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（細音說，方法有分成本與效益）<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"cad27be28df758fe5ee7ea6c7cbeb1badde254d2","tid":1461091,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6be5f3598f237779a6a68d8fb36c7fda2988dfe6","tid":1461091,"uid":248404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"尋日唔洗番？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"2b0c1f4df471b1e54d6d7ce92e9b0b83f257f532","tid":1461091,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"機場 見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef43bb2aa92a00132be92486d5eb8e1e8ba74a4a","tid":1461091,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n 有無人check過自殺求助嘅熱線work唔work<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459506\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459506</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區女<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FgXWuUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgXWuUM.jpg&h=6e8aad15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\npdf:<br />\n<a href=\"https://we.tl/t-zkYuY8ShZJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwe.tl%2Ft-zkYuY8ShZJ&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=4c31cc2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://we.tl/t-zkYuY8ShZJ</a>"}]}